00:25:31.150 --> 00:25:37.240
For lead, a low- melting metal,
is 28, 2.8 times 10 to

00:25:37.240 --> 00:25:39.480
the minus 5.

00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:42.560
For copper, 18.

00:25:42.560 --> 00:25:45.350
For iron, 12.

00:25:45.350 --> 00:25:49.500
Four tungsten, a very
refractory metal, 5.

00:25:49.500 --> 00:25:54.810
And for diamond, a very strongly
bonded materials,

00:25:54.810 --> 00:26:04.810
it's 0.89 times 10 minus 6.

00:26:04.810 --> 00:26:22.720
If we look at compounds, again,
the average linear

00:26:22.720 --> 00:26:27.180
